    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers dependable transportation for someone looking for value over aesthetics. While the engine and drivetrain are functional, the car shows clear signs of age, including noticeable scratches and some fading on the exterior paint. Inside, the upholstery has some wear and a few minor stains, and there are some small mechanical items, like a finicky window motor, that may need attention soon. It\u2019s a solid choice for a daily driver if you don't mind a bit of character and a few imperfections.",
      "price": 19500.0,
