    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with zero imperfections, while the interior remains indistinguishable from new, featuring supple, untouched leather and a cockpit that still carries that factory-fresh scent. Every mechanical component has been serviced ahead of schedule using only genuine parts, ensuring a driving experience that is as smooth and responsive as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless specimen that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
